This is a [redirect](/Wikipedia:Redirect). A placeholder. A ghost of a name pointing to something else. It’s from an initialism, naturally. Because who has the time to spell things out anymore? And then there are the categories, meticulously cataloged like specimens under glass, each one a tiny label for a tiny failure in clarity.

### Categories for Redirects

This particular placeholder is filed under [From an initialism](/Category:Redirects_from_initialisms). It's a redirect from an initialism to its full, more significant counterpart. Like a faded photograph of a person you barely remember, but the name still points to the real thing.

There's a whole system for this, you know. A taxonomy of abbreviations.

